    "If students frequently interact with these tools, they might inadvertently adopt undesirable behaviors.",
    "For instance, if the assistant consistently responds to inappropriate comments in a passive or subservient manner, it might indirectly encourage behaviors such as sexism (Zhou, 2023).",
