    "Incorporating ChatGPT into research fields may unintentionally perpetuate biases present in its foundational data.",
    "For instance, in medical and health research, if patient data does not appropriately remove potentially biased information (like gender, racial background, or income), the analysis might reflect related societal biases (Abd-Alrazaq et al., 2023; Corsello & Santangelo, 2023; Karabacak et al, 2023; Master, 2023; Witte et al., 2023)."
